Utility wallet

Mywallets is a chrome-extension wallet for easily managing your Utnet utility accounts

Mywallets is the first chrome-extension wallet exclusive for the Utility blockchain.

* Integrated Liquid Staking via Metapool.app
* Lockup Accounts Support
